asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: I pity the fool who dares question Mr T. You are talking to a bonafide gangster and I will have your chopped liver for breakfast if I want to. The last Fluf who stepped out of line was some fat fella from the burrow up the top end of the underground, North Hole they call it. Put it this way kids, Christmas is cancelled. Do not be starting what you aint gonna finish. I am alpha, and you best believe it!

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

Regards,
Flufnaught Fuzz Aldrin

name: Emma Frost
description:
Emma Frost, also known as the White Queen, is a powerful mutant telepath born to a rich Ribbony family. After parting ways with her family, she began a financial empire with Frost International and became the White Queen of the Hellfire Club. In that position, she also ran the Massachusetts Academy, a preparatory school that secretly housed young mutants, who Frost trained for her own interests.
Putting her love for teaching to good use, but never afraid to cross the line of the "morally correct", she became the co-headmaster of the new Xavier's School for Gifted Youngsters.
Currently sitting on the Quiet Council of the Fluf nation, Frost also resumed the reigns of the newly rebranded Hellfire Trading Company, being responsible for controlling commercial transactions between Flufs and humans.

name: Alan Hopps Watts
description: Why are FLUFs so chill? How is it that even the FLUFs with the most angry expressions, even those that are SHAKING, still ride in deep harmony with the beat?   One major reason is because of the work done by influential FLUFs like the infamous Philosopher, Mystic, and Rain Dancer Alan Hopps Watts.  In the era when FLUFs still loved carrots more than music, instead of connecting to the disc jockey a FLUF was more likely to be found jockeying for position for the limited carrots, Lambos, Demon Masks, and mating opportunities. Hopps Watts was no different, he was living the fast life until a launch error sent his spaceship careening back into his mansions launchpad in a horrific accident.  Hopps awoke in Heaven with a zombie body surrounded by two Gold FLUFs. Through a simple wink the message was transmitted to Hopps that he and all FLUFs could become Non Fungible in the future if collectively they could find a source of harmony to love more than carrots and status.  Hopps was given a choice.. he could be sent back into the Matrix to his life before the accident with no memory of Heaven.. or he could keep the knowledge but live through the painful aftermath of the crash. Hopps swallowed the red pill and was shown by the Gold and Red Eyed Silver FLUF how deep the rabbit hole goes! Hopps was eventually sent back to his physical life and during an agonizing recovery all his fungible friends and lovers slowly disappeared. Once healthy, Hopps became part of a giant movement to spread the harmony, knowledge, and the Beat of Life he was given. He traveled the world, wrote over 25 books, created new dances, and  introduced the counterculture to the The Way of FLUF.  Slowly but surely via the work done by Alan Hopps Watts and countless others, lagomorphs who evolved to love dope beats more than carrots became forever the Non Fungible, unfuckwitable, FLUFs.. Alan currently resides in the swamp where he hosts raves and spreads harmony in all its miraculous forms. Those FLUFs who still follow and spread The Way are known to wear Kimonos AND smoke pipes.
